text: Bangalaia bipunctipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1966. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia bipunctipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1966
